data.eml:eml: A new species of Leptolalax (Anura: Megophryidae) from northeastern Cambodia

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Rowley, Jodi J. L., Stuart, Bryan L., Thy, Neang, Emmett, David A. (2010): A new species of Leptolalax (Anura: Megophryidae) from northeastern Cambodia. Zootaxa 2567: 57-68, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.197318
